{"tid":2278104,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開心大發現 人嘅大腦真係好神奇","createTime":"2020-11-09T02:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T04:00:41.000Z","uid":255719,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"abd6b7f427c3e037554f2e5ced3715caf8eead40","tid":2278104,"uid":255719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"話說因為十一月所以小弟冇打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以今朝夢遺，發左個春夢<br />\n<br />\n小弟淨係試過口交，仲係青頭，仲要已經上世紀前，係個夢入面，連口交個感覺都係同真人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但當插入去個吓，就完全冇感覺，因為大腦知我未屌過閪，所以唔識整一個屌閪嘅感覺比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大腦真係神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f50a51f7b3df36df97ea88fd5f7bef24b120b43","tid":2278104,"uid":371039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"關我咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcacff7a4fd96cd57fe2582c6e994f44ffc8211","tid":2278104,"uid":255719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f50a51f7b3df36df97ea88fd5f7bef24b120b43","tid":2278104,"uid":371039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"關我咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:00:41.000Z","msg":"我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}